<br>
This is an alternate reality, an escape if you will, that in many ways surpasses that all-time master called BOOKS.  Are the hours spent reading wasted?  And better still, you direct your adventure in this living book.  If it gets boring, or repetitive, my guess is I know whose fault it is.<br>
<br>
Verant certainly isn't without fault, but so what.  Kudos to them for this masterpiece of entertainment.<br>
<br>
