<br>
Fenye, I can really relate to your post. I haven't been snow boarding for 2 years (not only because of EQ) and I intend to get back out there. Your other oppinions and observations were also right on. This would seem like a strange place to post this, but I feel like getting it out: I never grouped with you or really talked with you (my druid ported you once) so I don't know why people don't like you. You make posts to deliberately upset people and it is obvious that it works by the responses that you get, even from me. Now I can see the general irrationality that many EQ players are suffering from, even me.  Thanks for helping me take a step back and rethink some fine points of my life. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> /salute</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> <p><br>Pokis <br> 51 Rake<br>Officer of <B><A HREF="http://pub89.ezboard.com/bimperium32440">Imperium</A></B></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisbrellserilisdiscussion.showMessage?topicID=8277.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisbrellserilisdiscussion.showMessage?topicID=8244.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisbrellserilisdiscussion.threadControl?topicID=8137.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisbrellserilisdiscussion.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8137.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisbrellserilisdiscussion.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8137.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="t